{"title":"Hexo 网站初始化","date":"2022-04-25T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年4月25日","L":"2022/04/25","MM-DD":"04-25"},"link":"hexo-web-site-init","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2022-04-24T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<p>第一步</p>\n<p>初始化：<code>hexo init</code></p>\n<p>安装 主题<br>\n使用的主题：<code>inside</code><br>\n地址：<code>https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>进入博客目录 <code>project/</code> , 执行以下命令：</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-theme-inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>配置：<code>project/_config.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">inside</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>创建主题文件：<code>project/_config.inside.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<!-- https://github.com/omnibingo/talk2.it -->\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"个性化调整:\">个性化调整:<a title=\"#个性化调整:\" href=\"#个性化调整:\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>设置文章头高度:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>CSS文件: <code>styles.91e7dfca63c7c151daa6.css</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fn&#123;padding-top:37%</span><br><span class=\"line\">调整为:</span><br><span class=\"line\">fn&#123;padding-top:24%;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>去掉文章底部上一个下一个按钮</li>\n</ul>\n<p>JS文件: <code>main.543c891b4aad158701f3.js</code><br>\n找到以下代码属性拼接<code>1</code>即可<br>\n可根据关键字:<code>post.prev</code> <code>post.next</code>查找</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">uy</span>(<span class=\"params\">t, e</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp; t &amp;&amp; (<span class=\"title class_\">So</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;a&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">31</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Bo</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">xo</span>()), <span class=\"number\">2</span> &amp; t) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> t = <span class=\"title class_\">Do</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t.<span class=\"property\">ngIf</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"title class_\">No</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;routerLink&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;/&quot;</span>, t.<span class=\"pro